gin:0px;\">. De encontrar coincidencias</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">,</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> </span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">el sistema nos arrojará el</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> o los</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> candidato</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">s</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> a seleccionar</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> </span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">mediante</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> los </span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">parámetros</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> de consulta ingresados, con la</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">s</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> </span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">siguiente</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">s</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> característica</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">s</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">:&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;font-size:11pt;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span> </p> </div><ul><li style=\"clear:both;cursor:text;font-size:11pt;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"margin:0px;font-weight:normal;color:windowtext;text-align:left;\"><span lang=ES-AR style=\"margin:0px;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;\">Tipo de documento </span></span><span lang=ES-AR style=\"margin:0px;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;\">(</span><span style=\"margin:0px;background-position:0px 100%;background-repeat:repeat-x;border-bottom:1px solid transparent;\">select</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">)</span></span><span lang=ES-AR style=\"margin:0px;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;\"> (DNI-CUIT</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">/</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">CUIL-PASAPORTE</span><span style=\"margin:0px;\">-DNM-CIPL</span><span style=\"ma