</a>), se indica que los candidatos notificados son distintas. Desde esta acción se cambiará el estado a ambas personas en las notificaciones de auditoría&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;display:inline !important;\">de &quot;Pendientes&quot; a &quot;Diferenciado&quot;.&nbsp;</span></span></span> </p><p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;display:inline !important;\"><br></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span><span lang=ES style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=ES style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;\"></span> </p><p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span><b><span lang=ES style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">Link de pantallas:</span></b></span><span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;\"></span> </p><p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/49a2a3de-c7d6-40bd-a8be-b9cbe35fd440-1cf1/screen/e0fe070e-dfe5-4225-bb2b-8614ab5ca156/\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">pantalla 1</a>: Detalle de duplicados.&nbsp;<br></span></span> </p><p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/49a2a3de-c7d6-40bd-a8be-b9cbe35fd440-1cf1/screen/7684f2f5-814c-4a0d-9d4b-ebca1a9f5a6d/\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">pantalla 2</a>: Mensaje de Personas diferentes.&nbsp;<br></span></span> </p><br> </div>","acceptanceCriteria":"<div><ul><li>Dado que, se identifico que las personas son diferentes, se debe cambiar el estado de &quot;<span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:start;display:inline !important;\"><span style=\"display:inline !important;\">Pendientes</span>&quot; a &quot;Diferenciado&quot; para excluirlos del listado de notificados.&nbsp;</span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:start;display:inline !important;\">Se notificará mediante un tooltip que: Se diferenció a las personas: Persona 1 y Persona 2 (igual que en la fusión, ver <a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/49a2a3de-c7d6-40bd-a8be-b9cbe35fd440-1cf1/screen/7684f2f5-814c-4a0d-9d4b-ebca1a9f5a6d/\">pantalla 2</a>)</span> </li> </ul> </div>","taskCount":0,"tasks":[]},{"id":6017,"type":"Product Backlog Item","title":"6. HdU- Consulta de detalle de auditados","state":"Approved","areaPath":"ODI\\ODI Team Tecnologia","iterationPath":"ODI","assignedTo":"Martin Miguel Diaz Maffini","description":"<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin:0px 0cm 0.0001333px;\"><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;clear:both;cursor:text;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:12px;\"><div lang=ES-MX style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;color:windowtext;text-align:left;\"><span lang=ES-ES style=\"box-sizing:border-bo