tyle=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:windowtext;margin:0px;font-size:11pt;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:700;text-align:left;display:inline !important;\">Quiero:</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:700;text-align:left;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">&nbsp;Tener la opción de editar la gestión de cupos de un bloque de programación.</span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></span> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display:inline !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;\"><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;clear:both;cursor:text;\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:12px;margin:0px 0px 10.6667px;color:windowtext;text-align:left;\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span lang=ES-AR style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;font-size:11pt;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bold;display:inline !important;\">Para</span><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Modificar las reglas y/o condiciones de los cupos del bloque horario de una agenda.&nbsp;</span></span></font> </p> </div> </div></span> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration:underline;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, 