er-box;\"><span lang=ES style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;background:white;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display:inline !important;\">Total Tarjeta Debito ($)</span>&nbsp;=</b>&nbsp;Se s<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display:inline !important;\">uma los movimientos con<span>&nbsp;</span></span>tarjeta de débito.</span> </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span lang=ES style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;background:white;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Total Cheques<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;</span></span>($) =</b><span>&nbsp;</span>Se suma los movimientos con medio de pago “cheque”.</span> </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span lang=ES style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;background:white;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Total Transferencia ($)</b><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&nbsp;=</b>&nbsp;</span>Se suma los&nbsp; movimientos con medio de pago “transferencia”.</span> </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span lang=ES style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;background:white;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Total QR ($) =</b><span>&nbsp;</span>Se suma los movimientos cobrados con medios con código QR, Aplica a todos los servicios de QR habilitados.</span> </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span lang=ES style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;background:white;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Total General ($)</b><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&nbsp;=&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Total Efectivo $ + Total Tarjeta $ + Total Cheques $ + Total Transferencia $ + Total QR $ Representa la suma de todos los medios de pago.</span> </li> </ul></span></span><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:14.6667px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></span></font><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><font fac