mprobante","state":"Ready","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":16932,"type":"Task","title":"FE - Modal imprimir comprobante","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Diego Gimbernat","description":""},{"id":22818,"type":"Task","title":"Code Review","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Marco Alex Brusa","description":""},{"id":17430,"type":"Task","title":"DT - modificacion interfaces","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Diego Alejandro Nuñez","description":""},{"id":16933,"type":"Task","title":"QA-Diseño de Casos de prueba","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":17057,"type":"Task","title":"BE - Descargar comprobante","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Lucas Ezequiel Ayala","description":""},{"id":23563,"type":"Bug","title":"QA - Diferencia en el diseño en el comprobante","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":16687,"type":"Task","title":"Diseño tecnico","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Diego Alejandro Nuñez","description":""},{"id":15148,"type":"Task","title":"UX - Diseño de mockup","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Melanie Garcia","description":"<div>Link de pantallas&nbsp; </div><div><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/6cb917c4-87bc-484a-9dd1-05a8e969288c-39ea/\">https://xd.adobe.com/view/6cb917c4-87bc-484a-9dd1-05a8e969288c-39ea/</a><br> </div>"},{"id":23216,"type":"Bug","title":"QA - No se visualiza el Modal de comprobante","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":17055,"type":"Task","title":"BE - Modificar Admision","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Lucas Ezequiel Ayala","description":""}]},{"id":14436,"type":"Product Backlog Item","title":"Mejora de campo número de documento","state":"New","areaPath":"ODI\\ODI Team Tecnologia","iterationPath":"ODI","assignedTo":"Natalia Gorriti","description":"","acceptanceCriteria":"","taskCount":0,"tasks":[]},{"id":14493,"type":"Product Backlog Item","title":"Listar los cargos por cobrar y cobrados a pacientes con pago particulares","state":"Done","areaPath":"ODI\\ODI Team Admision","iterationPath":"ODI\\R-01\\Sprint 28","assignedTo":"Geroan Antonio Cadenas Alvarez","description":"<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">Como:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">Gestor de caja&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"></span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">Quiero:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\">Listar los cargos por cobrar y conrados a pacientes\ncon pagos privados. <span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<br><b>Para:</b>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Gestionar los cobros en caja por paciente.</span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\"></span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><b><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\">Descripción y comportamiento:</span></u></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\">&nbsp;Desde el módulo de caja se\nrequiere consultar y listar los cargos pendientes por cobrar a pacientes que se encuentran\nen proceso para ser admitidos, así como los cargos ya cobrados.&nbsp;</span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\">La consulta de pacientes con cargos pendientes (valor a pagar), se deriva de la acción de eventos de cobros a privados ejecutados desde la HU:<a href=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/ODI/_workitems/edit/14040\" tabindex=0 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 90, 158);border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;outline:transparent;text-decoration:underline;transition:color 80ms cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), background 80ms linear;font-size:14px;text-align:start;\">Item 14040</a><span style=\"font-size:14px;text-align:start;display:inline !important;\">: Evento cobro a privado y&nbsp;</span>puede generar dos posibles escenarios.</span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><b>Escenario 1</b>) Se encontraron pacientes con cargos.&nbsp;</span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Se debe listar a los pacientes teniendo en cuenta el siguiente orden de la grilla:&nbsp;</span></span> </p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 8pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"> </p><ul><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Fecha&nbsp;</span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Hora turno</span></span> </li><li><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\">Episodio (puede venir vacío)</font> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Paciente</span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Documento</span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Financiador</span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Servicio</span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Efector</span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Estado de pago</span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Menú contextual</span></span> </li> </ul><div><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\">ORDEN DEL LISTADO (ESTANDAR):</font> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">El listado debe estar ordenado por Estado, priorizando en primer orden los </span><b style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Estados Pendientes</b><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"> segun </span><u style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">orden de creacion del evento de cobro. </u><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Luego debe seguir con los Estados Cobrados, por orden según hora de cobro (sistema)</span> </div><div><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><br></font> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\">Una vez listado los pacientes se debe permitir:&nbsp;</span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><ul style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><li><span style=\"font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\">Filtrar por tipo y número de documento&nbsp; (Se debe permitir filtrar por DNI y número de documentos del listado pre establecido)</span> </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\">Botón Emitir Pago - Este evento se desarrollará en HU&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/ODI/_workitems/edit/11958\" tabindex=0 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 90, 158);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer;border-radius:2px;outline:transparent;transition:color 80ms cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), background 80ms linear;font-size:14px;text-align:start;\">Item 11958</a><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:14px;text-align:start;display:inline !important;\">: Emitir Cobro a Privados)</span></span> </li> </ul><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/1ca9bb62-2adf-4aa4-a3f2-0c7a19960c50?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><br> </div> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"></span> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/52e17e0f-4bf1-4b0c-aa78-50ef0093447a?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br></span> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"><br></span> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"><br></span> </div><div style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><br> </div><span style=\"color:black;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;\">Escenario 2</b><span style=\"font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\">)<span>&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline !important;\">No hay pacientes con cargos disponibles.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;text-align:justify;\"><br></span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;text-align:justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Se debe mostrar un mensaje informando que no hay cargos pendientes por cobrar, ver mockup.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\"><span><span style=\"display:inline !important;\"><br></span></span></span></span></span><br><br><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/9dcf28f8-4332-4b02-9c9d-6eaad8bec366?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image> </div><div><br> </div><div>Caso cuando se buscar por paciente y este no tiene cargos por cobrar i cobrados.&nbsp;<br><p> </p><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/3be2fda2-f383-4b48-87ba-f77c965fc522?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;display:inline !important;\"><br></span> </div><div><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;display:inline !important;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/be9aaf52-6492-4c5f-868c-de12e4a4118d-ebc9/\" style=\"box-sizing:border-b