l, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;display:inline !important;\"><span style=\"display:inline !important;\">Estado de Pago.</span><br></span></span></span></span> </li><li><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;display:inline !important;\">Fecha y horas de la atención.</span></span></span></span> </li><li><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;\">Financiador y plan aplicado.</span> </li><li><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;display:inline !important;\">Detalle de práctica (fecha, <span style=\"display:inline !important;\">práctica, cantidad<span>&nbsp;</span></span>y valor)</span></span></span></span> </li><li><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;display:inline !important;\">Total a pagar</span></span></span></span> </li><li><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:black;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;display:inline !important;\">Medios de pagos.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span> </li> </ul><p> </p><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><font face=\"Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:14.6667px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span></span></span></span></span></font> </div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\">Ver Mockup</span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\"><br></span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\"><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/b44ecafc-eff4-4641-9bab-1b5fa5c9dc02?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br></span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\"><br></span><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"> </span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\"><br></span><span style=\"color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"> </span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;color:rgb(200, 38, 19);\"></span> </div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/c1650953-38d2-4d4f-bc79-321ac536c8d6?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\"><br></span> </div><div><br> </div><div> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14.6667px;text-align:justify;display:inline !important;\">Link a prototipo:&nbsp;<div><table width=582 style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:437pt;\"><colgroup><col width=582 style=\"width:437pt;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr height=28><td width=582 height=28 style=\"padding-top:1px;padding-right:1px;padding-left:1px;color:black;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;vertical-align:bottom;border:none;color:rgb(5, 99, 193);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:middle;width:437pt;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/a92233f7-33fa-4592-b668-cf8e3365531d-fc71/\">https://xd.adobe.com/view/a92233f7-33fa-4592-b668-cf8e3365531d-fc71/</a> </td></tr></tbody></table> </div></span> </div>","acceptanceCriteria":"<div><ul><li>Se debe visualizar el estado de pago actual.&nbsp; </li><li>Debe ser scrolleable en caso de que los conceptos sean muchos.&nbsp; </li> </ul> </div>","taskCount":4,"tasks":[{"id":17111,"type":"Task","title":"UX Mockup Detalle de pago","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Giselle Daniela Vazquez","description":"<table width=872 style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:654pt;\"><colgroup><col width=290 style=\"width:218pt;\"><col width=582 style=\"width:437pt;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr height=28><td width=290 height=28 style=\"padding-top:1px;padding-right:1px;padding-left:1px;color:black;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;vertical-align:bottom;border:none;vertical-align:middle;width:218pt;\">Mockup.&nbsp;<br><br><div><table width=582 style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:437pt;\"><colgroup><col width=582 style=\"width:437pt;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr height=28><td width=582 height=28 style=\"padding-top:1px;padding-right:1px;padding-left:1px;color:black;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;vertical-align:bottom;border:none;color:rgb(5, 99, 193);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:middle;width:437pt;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/a92233f7-33fa-4592-b668-cf8e3365531d-fc71/\">https://xd.adobe.com/view/a92233f7-33fa-4592-b668-cf8e3365531d-fc71/</a> </td></tr></tbody></table> </div><br> </td><td width=582 style=\"padding-top:1px;padding-right:1px;padding-left:1px;color:black;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;vertical-align:bottom;border:none;color:rgb(5, 99, 193);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:middle;width:437pt;\"> </td></tr></tbody></table>"},{"id":17036,"type":"Task","title":"Análisis, diseño y escritura funcional","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Geroan Antonio Cadenas Alvarez","description":""},{"id":23306,"type":"Task","title":"QA-Ejecución de Casos de Prueba","state":"To Do","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":23305,"type":"Task","title":"QA-Diseño de Casos de Prueba","state":"To Do","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""}]},{"id":15965,"type":"Product Backlog Item","title":"Desconfirmar la Admision de un Paciente que haya realizado algun pago por atención","state":"Committed","areaPath":"ODI\\ODI Team Admision","iterationPath":"ODI\\R-01\\Sprint 31","assignedTo":"Marco Alex Brusa","description":"<div><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Como:</strong><span style=\"display:inline !important;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>Usuario del sistema de admisión (administrativo o admisionista)</span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div> </div><div> </div><div><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Quiero:</strong><span style=\"display:inline !important;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>Poder deshacer la acción que cambia el estado del paciente&nbsp; &quot;En sala de espera&quot; y validando que no haya pago realizado por paciente</span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Para:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>Volver al estado anterior &quot;Programado&quot; por si hubo alguna acción a corregir (UNDO) </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></b></span> </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></b></span> </div><h3 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:600;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Contexto funcional</strong> </h3>Como ya fue explicado en la HU&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/ODI/_workitems/edit/12306\" tabindex=0 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 90, 158);border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;outline:transparent;text-decoration:none !important;transition:color 80ms cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), background 80ms linear;font-size:12px;\">ITEM 12306</a>, es posible desconfirmar una admision cerrada. En dicha HU el circuito se da cuando el paciente no tiene que abonar nada, en esta HU se debe verificar primero que para des-hacer una admsión no haya un pago previo de parte del paciente. </div><div><br> </div><div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/65725929-1d46-4cfa-9aeb-6c6b6931dc96?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div><br> </div><div>Al seleccionar un paciente en estado &quot;Sala de Espera&quot; y querer volver a un estado anterior, el sistema debe verificar primero, si el paciente tiene un pago pendiente ver HU (<a href=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/ODI/_workitems/edit/12285\" tabindex=0 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 90, 158);border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;outline:transparent;text-decoration:none !important;transition:color 80ms cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), background 80ms linear;font-size:12px;\">ITEM 12285</a>). En realidad pueden darse 2 casos: </div><div><br> </div><div><b>CASO 1: ESTADO PENDIENTE DE PAGO:</b> </div><div><br> </div><div>Si el paciente tiene un pago pendiente, estado &quot;Pago Pendiente&quot;, la acción de volver a estado anterior se mantiene de la misma manera que la HU ya mencionada al incio de esta Historia (12306). De esa menera se debe anular el evento de CAJA generado al paciente como nueva condición. </div><div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/f85b23bd-c74f-41ab-bb3e-0eb2692bd1c4?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>CASO 2: ESTADO PAGADO</b> </div><div><br> </div><div>Si el paciente tiene un estado PAGADO (evento de caja), en este caso, no se podra generar la funcion de volver a estado anterior. En este caso el sistena debe generar un aviso de que existe un pago realizado del paciente y no podra volver al estado anterior. </div><div><br> </div><div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/16b5186b-a97e-4483-99fa-be6c50208aa3?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/23856a9c-f820-4746-ac02-b8afbe8dd3e1/_apis/wit/attachments/759579d9-0a31-4f9a-a31e-d9fb24dd4cab?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div>Para poder realizar la acción de volver al estado anterior, por proceso, primero se debe hacer la devolución de pago al paciente ver HU&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dev.azure.com/SofreDigital/ODI/_workitems/edit/16080\" tabindex=0 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 90, 158);border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;outline:transparent;text-decoration:none !important;transition:color 80ms cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), background 80ms linear;font-size:12px;\">ITEM 16080</a> </div><div><br> </div><div>Link mockup:&nbsp;<div><table width=582 style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:437pt;\"><colgroup><col width=582 style=\"width:437pt;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr height=43><td width=582 height=43 style=\"padding-top:1px;padding-right:1px;padding-left:1px;color:black;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;vertical-align:bottom;border:none;color:rgb(5, 99, 193);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:middle;width:437pt;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/f83ba0b1-ee65-42f6-8594-66d7c8b972f3-ad68/\">https://xd.adobe.com/view/f83ba0b1-ee65-42f6-8594-66d7c8b972f3-ad68/</a> </td></tr></tbody></table> </div> </div>","acceptanceCriteria":"<ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;padding:0px 0px 0px 40px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">El botón/acción<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">“Deshacer”</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>estará disponible solo si el estado actual del paciente es<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&quot;En sala de espera&quot;</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>y aún no fue llamado por el profesional. </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Al deshacer, el sistema deberá registrar el evento con el usuario que realizó la acción y la hora. </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">El estado del paciente debe volver a<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&quot;Programado&quot;</strong>, y reactivarse la posibilidad de edición de los datos/documentación. </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">El estado del Turno debe volver tambien a un estado anterior y pasar de<span>&nbsp;</span><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Consumido a Programado</b> </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">El<span>&nbsp;</span><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Encuentro</b><span>&nbsp;</span>generado, se debe anular de la base al deshacer la admision con esta funcionalidad </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">No debe afectar la integridad del turno ni provocar duplicación de datos. </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">El sistema deberá mostrar un mensaje de confirmación antes de deshacer la acción </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Esta funcionalidad estará disponible solo para perfiles autorizados. </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">El sistema debe validar si el paciente tiene un evento de pago pendiente o cobrado. </li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">No se podra volver a un estado anterior en caso de que el evento de pago este en estado &quot;Pagado&quot; </li> </ul><br>","taskCount":11,"tasks":[{"id":17323,"type":"Task","title":"AF","state":"In Progress","assignedTo":"Martin Casey","description":""},{"id":24265,"type":"Task","title":"BE - Listar cargos (release 1.3)","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Lucas Ezequiel Ayala","description":""},{"id":23959,"type":"Task","title":"QA-Diseño de Casos de Prueba","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":24047,"type":"Task","title":"FE - Habilitar \"opción volver a estado anterior\" en estado \"pend. pago\"","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Rodrigo Nicolas Bertin","description":""},{"id":24266,"type":"Task","title":"BE - Anular cargo pendiente de una admision","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Lucas Ezequiel Ayala","description":""},{"id":23960,"type":"Task","title":"QA-Ejecución de Casos de Prueba","state":"To Do","assignedTo":"Hernan Alexis Gutierrez","description":""},{"id":17324,"type":"Task","title":"ESC HU","state":"In Progress","assignedTo":"Martin Casey","description":""},{"id":23652,"type":"Task","title":"DT- Interfaces","state":"To Do","assignedTo":"Marco Alex Brusa","description":""},{"id":24267,"type":"Task","title":"BE - Cancelar admision (release 1.1)","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Lucas Ezequiel Ayala","description":""},{"id":23688,"type":"Task","title":"BD - Auditoría y estado de cargo","state":"In Progress","assignedTo":"Gustavo Cesar Tejerina","description":"<div><span><ul><li>Necesito un estado más para los cargos para saber si se anulo &quot;<span>Anulado&quot;</span> (hoy están solo pendiente/pagado). Se suman los estados &quot;Rechazado&quot; y &quot;Devolución&quot; </li><li>Necesito una tabla de auditoria para saber quien modifico el estado del cargo </li> </ul></span><br> </div>"},{"id":16246,"type":"Task","title":"UX - Diseño de mockup","state":"Done","assignedTo":"Giselle Daniela Vazquez","description":"<div><div><table width=582 style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:437pt;\"><colgroup><col width=582 style=\"width:437pt;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr height=43><td width=582 height=43 style=\"padding-top:1px;padding-right:1px;padding-left:1px;color:black;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;vertical-align:bottom;border:none;color:rgb(5, 99, 193);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:middle;width:437pt;\"><a href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/f83ba0b1-ee65-42f6-8594-66d7c8b972f3-ad68/\">https://xd.adobe.com/view/f83ba0b1-ee65-42f6-8594-66d7c8b972f3-ad68/</a> </td></tr></tbody></table> </div><br> </div>"}]},{"id":15967,"type":"Product Backlog Item","title":"Cambios de Estados de Pacientes de Forma Manual desde Admision","state":"New","areaPath":"ODI\\ODI Team Tecnologia","iterationPath":"ODI","assignedTo":"Natalia Gorriti","description":"","acceptanceCriteria":"","taskCount":2,"tasks":[{"id":16151,"type":"Task","title":"Análisis Funcional","state":"To Do","assignedTo":"Natalia Gorriti","description":""},{"id":16250,"type":"Task","title":"UX - Diseño de mockup","state":"To Do","assignedTo":"Melanie Garcia","description":"<div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Sprint 28 </div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Queda como pendiente y se pasa al prox sprint 29 - aviso de Martin C </div>- Comentario de 16-07 por nati y martin&nbsp; </div>"}]},{"id":15997,"type":"Product Backlog Item","title":"Tipos de Movimientos de Caja","state":"Done","areaPath":"ODI\\ODI Team Admision","iterationPath":"ODI\\R-01\\Sprint 28","assignedTo":"Geroan Antonio Cadenas Alvarez","description":"<div><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><b>Como: </b>Administrador&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">de caja&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:black;\"></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Quiero:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">Crear la tabla de tipos de movimientos de la caja.&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Para: </b><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Tener identificado los tipos de movimientos que debe realizarse en un caja.</span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">D</u></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><u style=\"font-weight:bold;box-sizing:border-box;\">escripción y comportamiento:</u><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&nbsp; Se requiere crear la tabla de tipos de movimientos de una caja, para poder clasificar e identificar de que evento se generó y su clasificación.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><br></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br></u></span></span></b></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Los tipos y clasificación&nbsp; de los movimientos a registrar en la tabla son:&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br></u></span></span></b></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><span style=\"display:inline !important;\"><b>TIPOS DE MOVIMIENTOS &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CLASE DE MOVIMIENTO&nbsp;</b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<b>CONCEPTO</b></span><br></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span>1) Cobro&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline !important;\">Ingreso&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cobro por atención&nbsp;</span></span></span></span> </p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><span>2) Fondo Inicial&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ingreso&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">Apertura de Caja</span><br></span></span></span></span> </p><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">3) Retiro por rendición&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Egreso&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">Cierre de Caja</span></span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\"><span>4) Ajuste de Apertura&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ajuste&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline !important;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>Ajuste de Apertura</span> &nbsp;<br></span><div>5) Ajuste de Cierre&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ajuste&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"display:inline !important;\">Ajuste de Cierre&nbsp;</span><br> </div></span> </div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\"><span>6) Retiro&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbs